## 🚀 Quick Reference Commands

### Docker Commands

```bash
# View all containers
docker ps -a

# View logs
docker logs <container-name> --tail 50 -f

# Restart container
docker restart <container-name>

# Remove container
docker stop <container-name> && docker rm <container-name>

# Clean up unused resources
docker system prune -af

# Check disk usage
docker system df

# Execute command inside container
docker exec -it <container-name> bash
```

### Jenkins Commands

```bash
# Get initial admin password
docker exec jenkins-server cat /var/jenkins_home/secrets/initialAdminPassword

# Restart Jenkins
docker restart jenkins-server

# View Jenkins logs
docker logs jenkins-server -f

# Backup Jenkins data
docker cp jenkins-server:/var/jenkins_home ./jenkins-backup
```

### SonarQube Commands

```bash
# View SonarQube logs
docker logs sonarqube-server -f

# Reset admin password (inside container)
docker exec -it sonarqube-server bash
cd /opt/sonarqube/bin/linux-x86-64
./sonar.sh reset-admin-password
```

### Troubleshooting Commands

```bash
# Check port usage
sudo netstat -tlnp | grep 8080

# Check Docker socket permissions
ls -l /var/run/docker.sock

# Verify Docker can be accessed
docker run hello-world

# Check disk space
df -h

# Check memory usage
free -h

# Check CPU usage
top
```

